    this  is  the  most  important  indirect tax reform in indias history  after the passage of this bill it will subsume 17 types of taxes levied by the central and the state governments and there will be a  uniform  goods  and  services  tax  in    the  entire  country    the  cost  of  the products  will  be  reduced  after  its  implementation    this  will  also  be  an important step to promote makein india  due to the increase in manufacturing sector more fdi will inflow in the country and it will economically strengthen the country    